        <div class="slide-body">
            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem;">100M+ people pay $20+/mo for AI &mdash; every one is a potential customer. Plus all the people who aren&rsquo;t using AI yet but want a great journaling app. Lower COGS than agentic platforms. Conservative projections given the scale of the opportunity.</p>
